Sharon Duncan-Brewster https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sharon_Duncan-Brewster 0 Sharon Duncan-Brewster is a British actress. She is perhaps best known for her role as Crystal Gordon in Bad Girls during the first four series, her role as Trina Johnson on EastEnders and her role as Maggie Cain in the autumn 2009 Doctor Who special, The Waters of Mars. She was also the voice over for Catherine Hunter in The Journey on FIFA 17, FIFA 18 and FIFA 19. Sharon_Duncan-Brewster is a_British_actress .
